{"tid":2072205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【課金撐新聞自由】和你撐壹週刊","createTime":"2020-06-20T12:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:51.000Z","uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"104cb766a48a396f79c71a4c2ba46c858a6a5e7a","tid":2072205,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/campaign/premium.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fcampaign%2Fpremium.html&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduRVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=2f5ee474\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fcampaign%2Fpremium.html&h=fe6fb54e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/campaign/premium.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「和你撐壹週刊」計劃是什麼？<br />\n自2019年7月起《壹週刊》推行訂閱制，我們一直秉承壹傳媒創辦人黎智英先生「讀者付最實惠的價錢，我們做最好的新聞」的宗旨來定價。因經營越見困難向外界告急後，我們收到無數忠實讀者的訴求，就是：你們定價太低！我們要求更多樣化定價和訂閱計劃！<br />\n<br />\n我們為了積極回應讀者訴求，<br />\n正是「和你撐壹週刊」計劃的誕生原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n另一原因，正是為了讓編輯和記者可以無後顧之憂去守護香港、<br />\n守護新聞自由，《壹週刊》需要更多彈藥。"},{"pid":"e145b8dba9c51e01282fe8ab1f8e110360f223fc","tid":2072205,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:08.000Z","msg":"課比蕭氏新聞台好似有用d"},{"pid":"1edbcaf6eae0033a383c40066ebabcdc82ad50be","tid":2072205,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎叫美國唔好制裁香港<br />\n2019年11月都仲話勇武係鬼<br />\n壹傳媒長期迫害勇武手足<br />\n真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}